font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">J </span></em></span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">。动量矩 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">L </span></em></span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">为常值时，角速度 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>ω</em></span><em> </em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">与</span>惯性矩 <em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">J </span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">代入，化作</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">                                                                    <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202112/25/154005k5w1hh1w8wvziw1h.png" title alt="动量2.png" width="77" height="65" style="width: 77px; line-height: 150%;">因此在动量矩 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">L</span></em></span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"> </span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">守恒条件下，当</span>惯性矩 <em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">J </span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">减小使角速度增大时，动能也随之增大。或与此相反。根据动能定理，质点系动能的变化是外力和内力做功的共同结果。握哑铃人在改变姿态时，外力来自哑铃的重力，内力来自双手对哑铃的握力。其中重力功 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">W</span></em></span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><sub>g </sub></span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">的正负号很容易确定，哑铃向下运动时作正功，向上运动时作负功。内力功 </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">W<sub>i </sub></span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">则必须根据握力和运动方向是一致还是相反来作出判断。外力和内力的总功为二者之和，</span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em></span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">= <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em><sub>g</sub></em>+<em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em><sub>i</sub></em>。其正负号决定了能量是增大还是减小。具体分析以下两种情况：</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">情况一：惯性矩<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">减小，输入功为正值，角速度和动能均增大。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">状态 (a) 转变为状态 (b)，即双臂平举变为双臂收缩，重力功 <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em><sub>g </sub></em><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;">= 0</span>。为克服离心力使哑铃产生向内运动的加速度，握力与运动的方向一致，内力功 <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em><sub>i </sub></em><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;">> 0</span>。总功 <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em> </em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 28px;">> 0</span>。</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">状态 (a) 转变为状态 (c)，即双臂平举变为双臂下垂，重力功 </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em><sub>g </sub></span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 28px;">> 0</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">，为使双臂产生下垂的加速度，握力必小于重力，所作的负功小于重力的正功。双臂为克服离心力向内收缩所作的功为正功。仍满足总功 </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W </span></em></span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 28px;">> 0</span>。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; font-size: 16px;">情况二：惯性矩<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; line-height: 150%;">增大，输入功为负值，角速度和动能均减小。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; line-height: 150%;"></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">状态 (b) 转变为状态 (a)，即双臂收缩变为双臂平举，重力功 </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em><sub>g</sub></span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><sub> </sub></span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">= 0</span></span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">，克服离心力的握力和运动方向相反，但产生向外运动加速度的握力和运动方向一致。若后者小于前者，则总功 </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em> </span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%; font-size: 20px;">< 0</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">状态 (c) 转变为状态 (a)，即双臂下垂转变为双臂平举，重力功 </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em><sub>g </sub></span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 28px;">< 0</span>，向上提升的握力必须超过重力，才能产生向上的加速度，其正功必大于重力的负功。但为克服离心力向外运动的握力作负功，仍能满足总功 </span><em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><span style="line-height: 30px;">W</span></em> </span></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 28px;">< 0</span>。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;"></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">上述茹科夫斯基凳实验表明，质点系的动量与动能是两个不同的概念。动量或动量矩守恒，动能很可能不守恒。动量的变化只能由外力或外力矩引起，内力不能改变动量或动量矩。动能的变化来自外力或内力所做的功。就改变系统动能的效果而言，外力与内力并无区别。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 24px;">2</span></strong><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 24px;">．</span><strong>美国首个卫星<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 24px;">倾覆</span>事故</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";">1958 年，美国首个卫星探险者一号（ Explorer-1 ）的倾覆事件是动量矩守恒，内力导致动能不守恒的又一例子。探险者一号是一个带有 4 根挠性天线绕极轴自旋的细长轴对称体（图 2）。按照经典刚体动力学的分析结论，不计太空中极其微弱的干扰力矩，刚体绕质心的动量矩和动能均守恒。其绕最小或最大惯性矩主轴的转动都应稳定。但探险者一号升空后，旋转轴逐渐翻转 90<sup>0</sup>，最终转变为绕赤道轴旋转而失效。如何解释这一违背经典力学结论的现象，成为当时力学界的热门话题。最后讨论清楚，虽然不存在外力功，但 4 根挠性天线变形产生的内阻尼所做的内力功使动能趋于减小，乃是倾覆事故的根本原因。</span><br></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">无力矩作用的刚体定点运动在经典力学中称为欧拉情形刚体定点运动。刚体绕过定点的任一惯性主轴均可做持续的匀速转动，称为永久转动。以<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;">定点</span> <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>Z</em></span><em> </em>轴。设刚体为轴对称体，以 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>z</em></span><em> </em>轴为极轴，赤道平面与 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;">(<em>X, Y</em>) </span>平面的交线为 <em>x </em>轴，组成主轴坐标系<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"> (<em>O-xyz</em>) </span> (图 3)。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 24px;">． 动量与动能：度量运动状态的两种指标</span></strong></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify;">     </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify;">关于动量和动能两种概念，哪个概念能作为运动状态合理的度量，在力学史中曾有过激烈争论</span><sup style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">[2]</sup><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify;">。法国数学家笛卡尔 (Descartes,R.) 于 1644 年最早引进动量概念（图 5）。他受物体弹性碰撞实验的启发，认为物体运动状态的强弱取决于质量 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">m </em></span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify;">与速度 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">v </em></span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify;">两个因素，应将二者的乘积 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">mv </em></span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify;">作为运动状态的度量。</span></span></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify;"><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt width="319" height="393" style="width: 319px; height: 393px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">图5  笛卡尔(Descartes,R.,1596-1650)</span></p><p style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;"><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="text-indent: 29px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">1686 年德国数学家莱布尼茨 (Leibniz,g.W.) 对此提出反对（图 6）。他将物体的质量 <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">m </em> </em>与速度平方<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"> <em>v</em></span><sup>2 </sup>的乘积 <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;">mv</em></em><sup>2 </sup>称为物体运动的 “活力” (拉丁文 vis viva)，认为度量运动状态的不是动量 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>mv</em></span>，而是活力 <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;">mv</em></em><sup>2</sup>。于是开启了笛卡尔派与莱布尼茨派之间延续数十年的争论。</span></p><p style="text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent: 29px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";">图6   莱布尼茨 (Leibniz,g.W.,1646-1716)</span></p><p style="text-indent: 29px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent: 29px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"></span></p><p style="text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">直到 1743 年，法国学者达朗贝尔 (d’Alembert,J.R.) 在他的著作《Trait<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">é</span> de dynamique》里对这场争论做了确切的总结（图 7）：</span></p><p style="text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">“ 对于量度一个力来说，用它给予一个受它作用而通过一定距离的物体的活力，或者用它作用一定时间的物体的动量同样都是合理的。”</span></p><p style="text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent: 29px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt width="285" height="341" style="width: 285px; height: 341px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";">图7  达朗贝尔(d’Alembert,J.R., 1717-1783)</span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"> 因此这场争论只是对不同力学概念的一场无谓的争论。就物体运动状态的量度而言，笛卡尔的动量是按力作用时间的量度，莱布尼茨的活力是按力作用距离的量度。二者并无冲突。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">   </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";">动能的定义最终于 19 世纪 20 年代完成。法国学者科里奥利 (Coriolis,G.G.) 引进了功的概念，建立了动能定理：力对物体做的功等于动能的增量。因此活力 <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;">mv</em></em><sup>2 </sup>前面必须增加 1/2，作为动能的确切定义 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>T </em>= <em>mv</em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><sup>2</sup></span>/2</span>，方能使动能定理得到满足：</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";">                                                                     <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202112/25/163316p1jlu42b36bku6mz.png" title alt="动量14.png" width="183" height="66" style="width: 183px;
